data.description: MUST SEE! Spacious home offers 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath in this Dublin community! Foyer offers high ceilings, New vinyl floor through out leading into a great room and open kitchen concept with tons of natural light, perfect for entertaining. Kitchen offers stainless appliances. First floor also offers a flex dining/office space. Upstairs offers laundry room, Primary suite with generous size walk in closet and attached bath with soaking tub and shower. Basement includes fully renovated finished living area with built in bar, storage, TV area, really great area to watch sports or movies and Gym. Back yard offers surrounding trees for privacy and patio with pergola/pavilion includes attached tv mount.
